summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending page 34-384 of the Seattle Municipal Code (Plat 67 W, page 161, Official Zoning Map, as adopted by Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property in Block 8, Burke Farrar's Columbia Park Addition to the City of Seattle from RD 5000 to BN. (Petition of John Demco, agent for Franklin Smith, C.F. 291444).
